Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to bolo za hluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam bežíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v poriadku, Aono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Nerob to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ani tu nieje...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam len mohla tá Mayuko zmiznúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O mňa sa nestaraj.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, včera som videla Vašu dcéru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-bola spolu s Yaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to povedala?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už si sa prebrala?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to, že žijem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcela si zomrieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre všetkých by bolo by lepšie, keby som tu nebola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy to tak bolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale tie deti ťa podla mňa hľadajú už celkom slušnú chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že tu nikto nieje.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toto miesto nieje normálne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spamätaj sa, Yorito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aonino origami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubujem, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdravím, tu je Ishizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nieje tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi išiel do mesta niečo kúpiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite sa čoskoro vráti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno... rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sem prišiel, hneď ti zavolám.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že mama o otec prídu neskoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neskoro chodia každý deň.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A v chladničke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Máme kari, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama mi to povedala ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... Máme ho oveľa viac než môžeme zjesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ja verím, že večerať spolu s ostatnými dokáže spraviť jedlo ešte lepším.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa mi to snažíš povedať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohli by sme zavolať Aono-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a navečerať sa všetci spolu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Nič som nepovedala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Páči sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevedela som, aké máš rada,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tak som kúpila z každého čo predávali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vezmi si koľko chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to všetko zjesť nemôžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáš ešte dosť síl na to, aby si jedla?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, o to nejde.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mnoho vecí sa stalo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a ja som premýšľala čo by som mala spraviť ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiež...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak dobre, asi by som najprv mala niečo zjesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rana otrhaným zajačikom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo za čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foie gras je moje.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ďakujem... že sa o mňa staráš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedať to so slzami v očiach je trochu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale asi máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvyšné onigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorito sa ešte nevrátil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pusti ma k nemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On tu nieje!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klameš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si to ty, kto klame?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to pred ním skrývaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do toho ťa nič nieje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to teda niečo, čo sa týka Matsuri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, dnes choď radšej domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tentoraz mi neutečieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne som na konci svojej púte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S týmto mečom a tvojou krvou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,budem môcť splniť sľub ktorý som kedysi dal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz, Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevolaj ma Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsujidou znie oveľa drsnejšie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Takeshi sa ľahšie vyslovuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... Na tom predsa vôbec nezáleží!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ty ma budeš volať Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, tak som to nemyslel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je presne ten dôvod, prečo nemáš žiadnych kamarátov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ty máš kamarátov, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som ti, aby si ma volala Tsujidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem... že si ma odprevadil domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš mi ďakovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budúci týždeň máš narodeniny, však, Kamikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je niečo, čo by si chcela?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem si želať čo chcem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, malo by sa to dať kúpiť z môjho vreckového.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nieje veľmi veľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proste mi rýchlo povedz, čo chceš k narodeninám!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plyšového zajačika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale veď už jedného máš a-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajačia rana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj hračky sa cítia osamelé, jasné?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uvidíme sa zajtra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\alpha&H40\c&HE5E5F6&\3c&H00006E&}Úbohé dieťa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\alpha&H40\c&HE5E5F6&\3c&H00006E&}Počula som, že to bolo vlámanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\alpha&H40\c&HE5E5F6&\3c&H00006E&}Celú rodinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\alpha&H40\c&HE5E5F6&\3c&H00006E&}Deti by sa nemali zabíjať...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si nezomrela?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to spravila...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydesila si ma na smrť!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj som zomrela.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stojíš rovno predomnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vraví sa im "yaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prišlo také čudné dievča a povedalo mi, že som zomrela a stala sa zo mňa yaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ale, nech si aj yaka alebo čo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stále si nažive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...už nemôžem ísť na slnko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už viac nie som človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja chcem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem sa do vášho sveta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerob to... Už nikdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ťa vrátim do sveta v ktorom si žila!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uvidíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubujem ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátim ťa naspäť, Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátim ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, zmizni!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemá cenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje schopnosti proti tomuto meču neúčinkujú!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubujem ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátim ťa naspäť, Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PRESTAŇ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ustúp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte kúsok...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte malí kúsok a-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmieš!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To už stačí!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takto to stačí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomocou jej krvi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,môže z teba byť zasa človek!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by som mala obetovať niekoho iného, radšej nechcem byť znova človekom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ale neznamená, že pre ňu obetujeme tvoje prianie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje prianie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neobetujeme ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje skutočné prianie bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:32.83,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}awai nami ni
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.07,0:19:32.83,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Unesená...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.21,0:19:44.48,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}...tichými vlnami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:44.48,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}saraware nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:20:00.96,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sotto sotto
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.29,0:20:00.96,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Jemne, jemne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:12.10,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}kietemo kamawanai kedo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.72,0:20:12.10,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}Prestáva mi záležať na tom, či zmiznem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:27.89,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs39}mada nokoru kimochi ha dokoka he
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:27.89,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fs39}Ostatné pocity niekam plávajú...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:38.88,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Ach... Strácajú svoje farby...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:38.88,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}aa iro wo otosu deshou
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:56.06,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}daremo shirazu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:56.06,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Plávajú nepovšimnuté,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:07.33,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}hi ga sasumadeni
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:07.33,Lyrics_A_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}tak dlho, kým len slnko svieti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľubujem ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátim ťa naspäť, Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A až do vtedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,budem stále pri tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priala som si len, aby si bol stále pri mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy láskavý Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,presne taký, ako vtedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:25.07,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}iroaseta peeji no kioku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:25.17,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Spomienky vpísané do vyblednutých stránok
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.49,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}hitomi tojireba yomigaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.66,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}vracajú sa vždy, keď privrieš oči
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:34.16,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}adokenai shoujo no inori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:34.19,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}a modlitba nevinného dievčaťa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:38.54,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}habatake yo kibou no sora he
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:38.75,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}letí až do neba, kde ešte existuje nádej.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:43.59,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}nageku mamonaku toki wa nagareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:43.64,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}I keď si vzdychneš, čas poletí ďalej,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:47.89,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}hitoritachi tomaru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:48.16,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ale zastaví sa pre tých, čo ostali sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:55.31,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yume mamoru shirabe kuchizusamu no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:55.43,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Nôtim si melódiu, čo chráni naše sny,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:59.65,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}hitobito ga nemuri ni tsukeba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:59.86,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}aby každý mohol zaspať sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:02.53,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}mata au hi no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:02.53,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Spať, túžiac znova sa stretnúť
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:07.70,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}negai tsumugeru deshou ai no ito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:07.70,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}a zamotať sa do vlákien lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:10.62,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yasashisa wo sasoru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:10.62,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Dobro zvíťazí tak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:17.87,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}otogibanashi anata kara osowatta no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:18.12,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ako v rozprávkach, o ktorých si mi rozprával.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.42,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}odorimashou sotto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:28.01,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Tak odtancujme spolu do našich spomienok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:27.84,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ano koro no omoi ni
